trans-unit.source: Enables the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Description.WebHttpBehavior"></xref> for an endpoint through configuration.
trans-unit.target: Aktiverer den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Description.WebHttpBehavior"> </xref> for et sluttpunkt ved konfigurasjon.

trans-unit.source: The WebHttpElement is a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.BehaviorExtensionElement> sub-type that can be used to include the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WebHttpBehavior> on an endpoint through configuration.
trans-unit.target: WebHttpElement er en <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.BehaviorExtensionElement>undertype som kan brukes til å inkludere i <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WebHttpBehavior>på et sluttpunkt ved konfigurasjon.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WebHttpBehavior> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.BehaviorExtensionElement>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WebHttpBehavior> behavior, when used in conjunction with the <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpBinding> binding, enables the Web programming model for a [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] service.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WebHttpBehavior>virkemåten ved bruk sammen med den <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpBinding>binder, gjør det mulig for nettserveren programming modellen for en [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] service.</xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpBinding> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WebHttpBehavior>

trans-unit.source: Note that the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Web.WebServiceHost> automatically adds this behavior to endpoints that use the <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpBinding>.
trans-unit.target: Legg merke til at <xref:System.ServiceModel.Web.WebServiceHost>automatisk legger til dette problemet til sluttpunkt som bruker <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpBinding>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpBinding> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Web.WebServiceHost>
